#: ml-slider.php:2068
msgid "Create slideshows with your Vimeo videos"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan video Vimeo Anda"

#: ml-slider.php:2072
msgid ""
"With Vimeo slides, you can build beautiful slideshows with your Vimeo "
"videos."
msgstr ""
"Dengan slide Vimeo, Anda dapat membuat tayangan slide yang indah dengan "
"video Vimeo Anda."

#: ml-slider.php:2076
msgid ""
"Vimeo slides will display your videos with auto play, mute, the ability to "
"hide controls, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Slide Vimeo akan menampilkan video Anda dengan pemutaran otomatis, suara "
"mati, kemampuan untuk menyembunyikan kontrol, dan banyak lagi."

#: ml-slider.php:2109
msgid "Create slideshows with your YouTube videos"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan video YouTube Anda"

#: ml-slider.php:2113
msgid ""
"With YouTube slides, you can build beautiful slideshows with your YouTube "
"videos."
msgstr ""
"Dengan slide YouTube, Anda dapat membuat tayangan slide yang indah dengan "
"video YouTube Anda."

#: ml-slider.php:2117
msgid ""
"YouTube slides will display your videos with auto play, mute, lazy load, "
"the ability to hide controls, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Slide YouTube akan menampilkan video Anda dengan pemutaran otomatis, suara "
"mati, pemuatan malas, kemampuan untuk menyembunyikan kontrol, dan banyak "
"lagi."

#: ml-slider.php:2150
msgid "Create slideshows with your posts"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan pos Anda"

#: ml-slider.php:2154
msgid ""
"With Post Feed slides, you can build slideshows with your latest posts, "
"events, or WooCommerce products."
msgstr ""
"Dengan slide Feed Pos, Anda dapat membangun tayangan slide dengan pos "
"terbaru, acara, atau produk WooCommerce Anda."

#: ml-slider.php:2158
msgid ""
"Post Feed slides will automatically display your posts with images, text, "
"custom fields, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Slide Feed Pos akan secara otomatis menampilkan pos Anda dengan gambar, "
"teks, bidang khusus, dan banyak lagi."

#: ml-slider.php:2193
msgid "Create slideshows with images stored outside of WordPress"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan gambar yang disimpan di luar WordPress"

#: ml-slider.php:2197
msgid ""
"With External URL slides, you can load images directly from non-WordPress "
"sources such as CDNs or image hosts."
msgstr ""
"Dengan slide URL Eksternal, Anda dapat memuat gambar langsung dari sumber "
"non-WordPress seperti CDN atau host gambar."

#: ml-slider.php:2201
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"External URL slides give you all the power of MetaSlider Slideshow, using "
"images stored anywhere you want."
msgstr ""
"Slide URL Eksternal memberi Anda semua kekuatan MetaSlider, menggunakan "
"gambar yang disimpan di mana pun Anda inginkan."

#: ml-slider.php:2236
msgid "Create slideshows with videos in your media library"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan video di perpustakaan media Anda"

#: ml-slider.php:2240
msgid ""
"With Local Video slides, you can build beautiful slideshows with videos in "
"your WordPress media library."
msgstr ""
"Dengan slide Video Lokal, Anda dapat membangun tayangan slide yang indah "
"dengan video di perpustakaan media WordPress Anda."

#: ml-slider.php:2244
msgid ""
"Local Video slides will display your MP4, WebM, and MOV videos with cover "
"images, auto play, mute, lazy load, the ability to hide controls, and much "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Slide Video Lokal akan menampilkan video MP4, WebM, dan MOV Anda dengan "
"gambar sampul, pemutaran otomatis, bisukan, pemuatan malas, kemampuan untuk "
"menyembunyikan kontrol, dan banyak lagi."

#: ml-slider.php:2279
msgid "Create slideshows with videos stored outside of WordPress"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan video yang disimpan di luar WordPress"

#: ml-slider.php:2283
msgid ""
"With External Video slides, you can add videos directly from non-WordPress "
"sources."
msgstr ""
"Dengan slide Video Eksternal, Anda dapat menambahkan video langsung dari "
"sumber non-WordPress."

#: ml-slider.php:2287
msgid ""
"External Video Slides will display your MP4, WebM, and MOV videos. Features "
"include text captions, cover images, auto play, mute, lazy load, the "
"ability to hide controls, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Slide Video Eksternal akan menampilkan video MP4, WebM, dan MOV Anda. Fitur "
"termasuk teks keterangan, gambar sampul, pemutaran otomatis, bisukan, "
"pemuatan malas, kemampuan untuk menyembunyikan kontrol, dan banyak lagi."

#: ml-slider.php:2322
msgid "Create slideshows with custom HTML"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan HTML kustom"

#: ml-slider.php:2326
msgid ""
"With Custom HTML slides, you can design slides using images, HTML and CSS. "
"This gives you complete control over the layout and styling."
msgstr ""
"Dengan slide HTML Kustom, Anda dapat merancang slide menggunakan gambar, "
"HTML, dan CSS. Ini memberikan Anda kontrol penuh atas tata letak dan gaya."

#: ml-slider.php:2361
msgid "Create slideshows with Tiktok Videos"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan Video TikTok"

#: ml-slider.php:2365
msgid ""
"A TikTok Slide will display a video in your slideshow directly from "
"TikTok.com."
msgstr ""
"Slide TikTok akan menampilkan video dalam tayangan slide Anda langsung dari "
"TikTok.com."

#: ml-slider.php:2428
msgid "Create slideshows with images from a folder"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan gambar dari folder"

#: ml-slider.php:2432
msgid ""
"The Image Folder slide type extracts images from a specified folder and "
"displays them as slides."
msgstr ""
"Tipe slide Gambar Folder mengekstrak gambar dari folder yang ditentukan dan "
"menampilkannya sebagai slide."

#: ml-slider.php:2436
msgid ""
"This slide type displays images from folders in your WordPress Media "
"Library."
msgstr ""
"Tipe slide ini menampilkan gambar dari folder di Perpustakaan Media "
"WordPress Anda."

#: ml-slider.php:2463
msgid "Create slideshows with Post Images"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan Gambar Pos"

#: ml-slider.php:2467
msgid ""
"The Post Images slide type extracts images from the current post and "
"displays them as slides."
msgstr ""
"Tipe slide Gambar Pos mengekstrak gambar dari pos saat ini dan "
"menampilkannya sebagai slide."

#: ml-slider.php:2471
msgid ""
"This slide type supports featured images, post content images, WooCommerce "
"galleries, Advanced Custom Fields images and galleries."
msgstr ""
"Tipe slide ini mendukung gambar unggulan, gambar konten pos, galeri "
"WooCommerce, gambar dan galeri Advanced Custom Fields."

#: ml-slider.php:2498
msgid "Create slideshows with your WooCommerce products"
msgstr "Buat tayangan slide dengan produk WooCommerce Anda"

#: ml-slider.php:2502
msgid ""
"With WooCommerce slides, you can build slideshows with your WooCommerce "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Dengan slide WooCommerce, Anda dapat membangun tayangan slide dengan produk "
"WooCommerce Anda."

#: ml-slider.php:2506
msgid ""
"WooCommerce slides will automatically display your products with images, "
"text, custom fields, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Slide WooCommerce akan secara otomatis menampilkan produk Anda dengan "
"gambar, teks, bidang kustom, dan banyak lagi."

